  "description": "<p>📍 Singapore | Full-Time | Entry-Level</p><p>We believe results are built in the right environment. You’ll work in a <strong>supportive, energetic, and closely-knitted team culture</strong> that values growth, accountability, and wins together.</p><p>Training, encouragement, and teamwork are part of daily life here.</p><p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Team players who thrive in positive, people-focused environments.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>😊 Positive attitude and strong teamwork</li><li>🤝 Supportive and collaborative mindset</li><li>🔥 Motivated and reliable</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>🎪 Work with a dynamic, energetic team</li><li>🤝 Support the team during campaigns/events</li><li>🎯 Contribute to team goals and success through ethical sales</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li>🌈 Fun, friendly, and supportive culture</li><li>👥 Strong team bonding and mentorship</li><li>🎉 Recognition and team celebrations</li><li>🚀 Travelling opportunities</li></ul>",
